<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="5Jan1933"><font color="red">5 January 1933</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I am glad to hear that he clings to his work so far as he can as a relief from the exhausting strain of the situation &hellip; Many thanks for having sent &hellip; from time to time pages of his MS, including the three enclosed with your present letter. </div>
